# Project core

- Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) before making changes
- Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS only — no npm, no frameworks
- Site at repo root; README is profile-only, not the live site
- Preview: `python3 -m http.server 8080`
- Deploy: push to `main` → GitHub Actions → https://sirbosssz.github.io
- Never force-push `main`
- Checkpoint handoff after each completed task (`~/.handoff/<repo-slug>/`)
- Stable facts → [docs/CONTEXT.md](../../docs/CONTEXT.md)
- Skills in `.agents/skills/`
